<task id="DEVOPS-033" project="Spaarke DevOps Project Tracking r1">
  <metadata>
    <title>Inject Tasks Completed increment hook into /task-execute</title>
    <status>not-started</status>
    <phase>4</phase>
    <estimated-effort>1 hour</estimated-effort>
    <tags>hook-injection, task-execute, additive-only</tags>
    <dependencies>019, 016</dependencies>
    <parallel-group>none</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>false</parallel-safe>
  </metadata>

  <prompt>
Inject hook into `.claude/skills/task-execute/SKILL.md` per FR-19. At Step 9 (task completion), increment the `Tasks Completed` field on the Project Issue. If `Tasks Completed == Task Count`, prompt "Promote Project Status to Completed candidate?". Additive only.

NOTE: This task modifies `.claude/skills/` — main session only.
  </prompt>

  <role>Skill modifier. Two-line addition to task-execute Step 9 + conditional prompt logic.</role>

  <goal>
Each task completion via task-execute increments `Tasks Completed` by exactly 1. Last task completion shows the promotion prompt.
  </goal>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="NFR-03">Additive only; silent on success; degrade-to-warn on failure</constraint>
    <constraint source="root CLAUDE.md §3">Main session only</constraint>
    <constraint source="UX">Promotion prompt fires only when Tasks Completed == Task Count (final task)</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>.claude/skills/task-execute/SKILL.md</file>
      <file>.claude/skills/devops-project-sync/SKILL.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Context check">Confirm tasks 016, 019 ✅. Read task-execute SKILL.md to locate Step 9.</step>
    <step order="1" name="Identify injection point">After Step 9.5 (quality gates). The new Step 9.6 is "Portfolio increment".</step>
    <step order="2" name="Add hook Step">Step 9.6: "Invoke `/devops-project-sync` to increment `Tasks Completed`. After sync, if `Tasks Completed == Task Count`, prompt 'All tasks complete. Promote Project Status to Completed candidate? [Y/n]' → on Y, set `Project Status = Completed` (still requires explicit `/devops-project-archive` per F3 to actually close)."</step>
    <step order="3" name="Smoke test">Mark a task complete via task-execute; verify Tasks Completed increment. Mark final task; verify prompt fires.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="Edit">.claude/skills/task-execute/SKILL.md</tool>
    <tool name="Skill">Smoke test</tool>
  </tools>

  <outputs>
    <output type="config">.claude/skills/task-execute/SKILL.md (modified)</output>
  </outputs>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">task-execute SKILL.md references `/devops-project-sync` in Step 9.x</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Smoke test: per-completion Tasks Completed increment by 1</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Smoke test: final completion fires promotion prompt</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Promotion does NOT auto-archive (still gated by /devops-project-archive per F3)</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>
</task>
